observe.desc:
      [
      { - There’s an old card attached to it.
'Merry Christmas! Santa rushes along the night sky to deliver presents to happy kids who don’t cry. Rudolf, the red-nosed reindeer, shines a light through the night fog while tugging a sleigh full of presents. All the happy kids in the world deserves a present!'}
